<!-- Rules Pop-up Container -->
<div id="rules-popup" class="rules-popup">
    <div class="rules-content">
        <span class="close-rules">&times;</span>
        <h2>Betting Rules</h2>
        <div class="rules-text">
            <h3>How to Play</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Multiple Timeframes: The game offers different timeframes to choose from:
                    <ul>
                        <li>30 seconds</li>
                        <li>45 seconds</li>  
                        <li>1 minute</li>
                        <li>2 minutes 30 seconds (150 seconds)</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Betting Window: Players can place their bets only until a specific time remains on the countdown, depending on the timeframe:
                    <ul>
                        <li>30 seconds timeframe: Betting closes when 5 seconds remain</li>
                        <li>45 seconds timeframe: Betting closes when 10 seconds remain</li>
                        <li>1 minute timeframe: Betting closes when 15 seconds remain</li>
                        <li>2:30 minutes timeframe: Betting closes when 30 seconds remain</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Selecting Numbers: Players must select any 3 buttons from the 9 available buttons (labeled 1 to 9).</li>
                <li>Bet Amount: After selecting 3 buttons, players must choose their betting amount and click the "Confirm" button to place the bet.</li>
                <li>Game Result: When the countdown reaches 0, the values of all 9 buttons will change randomly to one of the following:
                    <ul>
                        <li>0x (Zero Multiplier)</li>
                        <li>2x (Two Times Multiplier)</li>
                        <li>4x (Four Times Multiplier)</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Winning Calculation: The payout is determined based on the values assigned to the selected buttons.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Multiplier Rules</h3>
            <div class="rules-table-container">
                <table class="rules-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Selected Button Values</th>
                            <th>Multiplier</th>
                            <th>Payout Calculation</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>0x 0x 0x</td>
                            <td>0x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 0 (Loss)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>2x 2x 2x</td>
                            <td>4x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 4</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>4x 4x 4x</td>
                            <td>8x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 8</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>0x 0x 2x</td>
                            <td>0x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 0 (Loss)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>0x 0x 4x</td>
                            <td>0x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 0 (Loss)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>2x 2x 4x</td>
                            <td>2x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 2</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>2x 2x 0x</td>
                            <td>1.5x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 1.5 (Win)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>4x 4x 2x</td>
                            <td>4x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 4</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>4x 4x 0x</td>
                            <td>2x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 2</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>4x 2x 0x <span style="color:#33CC66;font-weight:bold;">(exact order)</span></td>
                            <td>1.5x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 1.5 (Win)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>2x 4x 0x</td>
                            <td>0x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 0 (Loss)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>2x 0x 4x</td>
                            <td>0x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 0 (Loss)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>0x 4x 2x</td>
                            <td>0x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 0 (Loss)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Any other combination with all different values</td>
                            <td>0x</td>
                            <td>Betting Amount × 0 (Loss)</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="example-text">
                <p><strong>Example:</strong>Suppose you select buttons 3, 5, and 7 and place a bet of ₹100. When the countdown reaches 0, the button values are assigned randomly.
                <ul>
                    <li>If your selected buttons get the values 4x, 2x, 4x, then according to the payout rules:</li>
                    <li>4x 4x 2x → Multiplier = 4x</li>
                    <li>Winnings = ₹100 × 4 = ₹400</li>
                </ul>
                
                <ul>
                    <li>If your selected buttons get the values 2x, 2x, 0x, then according to the updated rules:</li>
                    <li>2x 2x 0x → Multiplier = 1.5x</li>
                    <li>Winnings = ₹100 × 1.5 = ₹150</li>
                </ul>
                
                <ul>
                    <li>If your selected buttons get the values 4x, 2x, 0x (all different values), then:</li>
                    <li>4x 2x 0x → Multiplier = 0x (Loss)</li>
                    <li>Winnings = ₹100 × 0 = ₹0 (Loss)</li>
                </ul>
                
                <ul>
                    <li>If your selected buttons get the values 0x, 4x, 2x (all different values), then:</li>
                    <li>0x 4x 2x → Multiplier = 0x (Loss)</li>
                    <li>Winnings = ₹100 × 0 = ₹0 (Loss)</li>
                </ul>
                 
If your selected buttons got 0x, 4x, 0x, you would lose the bet because the payout for this combination is 0x.</p>
            </div>

            <h3>Important Notes</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Minimum bet amount: ₹10</li>
                <li>Maximum bet amount: ₹10,000</li>
                <li>Results are displayed every minute</li>
                <li>Winnings are credited instantly</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>




<!-- Referral Pop-up Container -->
<div id="referral-popup" class="popup">
    <div class="referral-content">
        <span class="close-referral">&times;</span>
        <h2>Your Referral Link</h2>
        <div class="referral-box">
            <div class="ref-link-container">
                {{#if user.referralCode}}
                <input type="text" name="reflink" id="refLink" value="https://bolrik.in/user/register?ref={{user.referralCode}}" readonly>
                {{else}}
                <p>No Referral Code Available</p>
                {{/if}}
                {{!-- <input type="text" id="refLink" value="{{user.referralLink}}" readonly> --}}
                <button id="copyRefLink" class="copy-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-copy"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="copyMessage" class="copy-message">Link copied!</div>
            
            <div class="referral-info">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">Total Referrals:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{#if user.referredUsers}}{{user.referredUsers.length}}{{else}}0{{/if}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">Earnings:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">₹{{user.referralEarnings}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="referral-rules">
                <h3>Referral Benefits</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Get 10% commission on every referral's first deposit</li>
                    <li>Earn 1% of your referral's every bet amount</li>
                    <li>Unlimited referrals allowed</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

